title: Morgan Agren's Conundrum - morganfan's CUT
description:
Hello,

this is an edited version of the documentary "Morgan Ågren's Conundrum - A Percussive Misadventure" by Carl King.

I decided to cut out all the parts I didn't enjoy (about 45 minutes of mostly non-Morgan stuff), using OpenShot Video Editor. I might re-upload with higher quality if there's demand.

"Morgan Agren's Conundrum" and "Conundrum UNDONE" are both available on Vimeo, you should buy/rent them if you haven't already.

Please support the inspiring artists Morgan Ågren and Carl King
